Blade and Pantra were plannng there next move when suddly 2 missles 
Blasted around them Blade and Pantra both dived sideways to another 
tree as the tree crashed to the ground "curses looks like our plan is 
going to have to change" blad ethought as he landed on another branch 
and looked up at his attacker

IronWing hovered in the air as he scanned the trees trying to find 
Blade and the traitor "get out here you traitor" he cried taking pot 
shots at the trees below him casting them into flames trying to find 
where they were hiding and almost at the same time Blade and Pantra 
jumped from the tree tops and grabed Ironwing by his leg and with 
they combinded power wiped him to the ground below with a large boom 
as he hit the ground, a cloud of dust floated in the air around the 
spot Ironwing hit

Blade and Pantra landed on the grass with a thud black mist formed in 
he hand and turned into a rifle at the same time pantra pulled her a 
pistol from her leg strap they both pointed it at Ironwings body as 
he layed on the ground face down "we can't have anyone missing up our 
plans" Blade said with smile "so that means we can't let u leave 
alive" pantra finished slowly pulling the trigger of her pistol
